replies.text:
@ThinkingandTinkering I love it!  My horrendous typing aside, I am looking forward to seeing your design.

I have always wanted a full height grandfather clock since I was a child.  By the time I was old enough to realize how much they cost, I determined one day to build one on my own.  I am thrilled to be joining your clock building adventure, and will hopefully be finalizing some of my current projects soon to start building mine.

Have fun with it!
